<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="233" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="4.[178,1085,492,572]" pageId="4" pageNumber="233">
Distribution and natural history: This species is currently known from two localities in 
<collectingRegion box="[480,586,521,543]" country="Laos" name="Phongsali" pageId="4" pageNumber="233">Phongsaly</collectingRegion>
and Oudom Xai provinces, North 
<collectingCountry box="[940,989,521,542]" name="Laos" pageId="4" pageNumber="233">Laos</collectingCountry>
(
<figureCitation box="[1003,1070,521,543]" captionStart="Map 1" captionStartId="3.[178,223,1064,1085]" captionTargetBox="[178,1054,211,1054]" captionTargetId="figure-1@3.[178,1054,211,1054]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="Map 1: Distribution of Tetrasticta laotica nov.sp." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5416219" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5416219/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="233">Map 1</figureCitation>
). The 
<typeStatus box="[224,268,551,572]" pageId="4" pageNumber="233">type</typeStatus>
specimens were collected at altitudes of approximately 1100 and 
<quantity box="[936,1016,550,572]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="4" pageNumber="233" unit="m" value="1500.0">1500 m</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
